Industrial Sensor Dashboard — Screenshot Submission Document

This document should be shared with interviewers/reviewers along with SCREENSHOTS_INDEX.html.

Screenshot checklist:
[ ] 01-dashboard-home.png
[ ] 02-sensor-cards-live.png
[ ] 03-plc-register-table.png
[ ] 04-live-chart.png
[ ] 05-backend-swagger.png
[ ] 06-docker-containers.png
[ ] 07-terminal-mqtt-sim.png
[ ] 08-terminal-modbus-sim.png

How to capture quickly on Windows:
1) Open each target page/terminal.
2) Press Win + Shift + S.
3) Save files in ./screenshots/ using exact names above.
4) Open SCREENSHOTS_INDEX.html in browser and verify every image loads.

How to share:
- Option A: Zip industrial-sensor-dashboard/ and send.
- Option B: Commit screenshots to GitHub branch and push.
- Option C: Print SCREENSHOTS_INDEX.html as PDF and share as one file.
